  "text": "Experimental conditions. Rats were injected IP with either KLH (300 g/kg; N ϭ 8) or an equivalent weight-adjusted volume of saline (N ϭ 4) and returned to their cages. This is the same dose of KLH used in Study 1. Four days after immunization, rats were killed rapidly by CO 2 asphyxiation. This time point was chosen on the basis of previous experiments showing decreases in IFN-␥ production by splenocytes from stressed animals 4 days after KLH immunization and stress [CITATION_1] .",
